<small>$OpenBSD: faq2.html,v 1.63 2003/08/08 14:05:05 nick Exp $</small>
@


1.63
log
@
Changes and updates inspired by mail.html changes...
* attempt to defend tech@@ from dweebs by removing from list of "more popular"
lists.
* pick a phrase, and stick with it: mail lists -> mailing lists (millert@@'s
preference)
* update with current info about subscribing.
* point people at the http://lists.openbsd.org
* <strong> -> <b>
* General rework.
