<h3>How do I display a man page source file? (i.e., one whose filename ends in a number, like tcpdump.8).</h3>
d341 1
a341 1
Note that [man_src_file] must be the man page source file (probably a file that ends in a number; i.e., tcpdump.8). The PostScript
